--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
INFORMATION
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This file lists changes made to the Ansible role. It follows semantic versioning
guidelines. The content is sorted in reverse chronological order and formatted
to allow easy grepping by scripts.

The fields are:
B: bug
C: change
E: enhancement
F: feature

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

* Version 0.6.0 (2020-11-29)
F: Add support for Monit service monitoring (node_exporter_monitor_monit_state)

* Version 0.5.1 (2020-11-19)
E: Ensure lineinfile tasks can create file if missing

* Version 0.5.0 (2020-10-19)
F: Add support for OpenBSD 6.8
F: Drop support for OpenBSD 6.7

* Version 0.4.0 (2020-08-23)
F: Configure --collector.textfile.directory flag on FreeBSD
B: Fix remove task variable on OpenBSD

* Version 0.3.0 (2020-08-18)
F: Create directories for --collector.textfile.directory
F: Configure --collector.textfile.directory flag on OpenBSD

* Version 0.2.0 (2020-05-19)
F: Add support for OpenBSD 6.7
F: Drop support for OpenBSD 6.6

* Version 0.1.0 (2020-04-08)
F: Initial release
